<h2>System Usage Guidelines</h2>
<p>Welcome to the Pahana Edu Bookshop Management System. This system is designed to streamline customer management, inventory tracking, and billing processes. Follow these steps to use the system effectively:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Login:</strong> Access the system using your provided username and password. Ensure you have the correct credentials from the system administrator. If you encounter login issues, verify your credentials or contact support.</li>
  <li><strong>Add Customer:</strong> Register new customers by navigating to the "Add Customer" page. Provide accurate details such as account number, full name, address, telephone number, and units consumed. Double-check entries to avoid errors in billing or customer records.</li>
  <li><strong>View Customers:</strong> Access the "View Customers" page to see a list of all registered customers. You can edit customer details, update contact information, or generate bills directly from this page. Use the search or filter options to locate specific customers quickly.</li>
  <li><strong>Manage Items:</strong> Use the "Manage Items" section to add new books, update existing inventory, or remove discontinued items. Ensure item details like title, author, price, and stock quantity are accurate to maintain inventory integrity.</li>
  <li><strong>Generate Bill:</strong> Create bills for customers based on their units consumed. Navigate to the "Generate Bill" section, select the customer, and verify the units consumed before generating the bill. You can print or save bills as needed.</li>
  <li><strong>Logout:</strong> Always log out after completing your tasks to ensure system security. Click the "Logout" link to exit the system safely.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Troubleshooting Tips</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Login Issues:</strong> If you cannot log in, ensure your username and password are correct. Reset your password via the "Forgot Password" link if necessary.</li>
  <li><strong>Data Not Saving:</strong> Check your internet connection and ensure all required fields are filled before submitting forms.</li>
  <li><strong>Bill Errors:</strong> Verify the units consumed and customer details before generating bills. Contact support if discrepancies persist.</li>
  <li><strong>System Slowdown:</strong> Clear your browser cache or try accessing the system from a different browser if performance issues occur.</li>
</ul>
